OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTougher taxi licensing     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frules come into force      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Tougher rules for taxi and private hire
OL,6, drivers will be introduced in England  
OL,7, in a bid to make passengers safer.     
OL,9,FDrivers who lose their licence in one  
OL,10,Fregion will be prevented from applying 
OL,11,Fto other local authorities without     
OL,12,Finforming them of their history.       
OL,14,FThree out of four council used the     
OL,15,Fnational database system voluntarily,  
OL,16,Fbut it becomes mandatory from Thursday.
OL,18,FTransport secretary Mark Harper said:  
OL,19,F"The safety of passengers, especially  
OL,20,Fwomen and girls, is paramount."        
